attack
Discworld combat help
attack

Name
.SI 5
attack - Co-ordinating attack function.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void attack();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This function co-ordinates the attacks on things.  It handles figureing
out who to attack, protection, people entering/leaveing the room.
Calling on a weapon, calling on the creature itself.  Adding xp for
the damage done.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
set_protector, set_concentrate, set_natural, query_protector, query_natural,
query_concentrate
.EP
